ts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/108642/', '', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole, Lidocaine, Tetracaine, Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, More', '', 1767369485);
